Requisites
========================================

* Python 2.5+
* Django 1.3
* pycrypto

Installation
========================================

Edit settings/60-local.pyconf for database settings.

Run python manage.py syncdb to setup database.
Run python manage.py runserver to start dev server and point browser to http://127.0.0.1:8000/

For quick testing purpose common.middleware.defaultuser.DefaultLoggedUser is active.
Use DEFAULT_USER and DEFAULT_USER_PASS in settings to change test user.
Remember to remove this middleware. 